{color:#000000}Machine Learning Services (In-Database) integrates R and Python with SQL Server, making it easy to build, retrain, and score models by calling stored procedures. Microsoft Machine Learning Server provides enterprise-scale support for R and Python, without requiring SQL Server.{color}

[https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/sql-server/sql-server-technical-documentation?toc=..%2ftoc%2ftoc.json&view=sql-server-2017]

